"Spectrum of Biological Modeling Methods" by Peter Sorger
A spectrum of methods applicable to biological pathways is illustrated from more abstact and
empircal on the left to more specific and mechanistic on the right. The bar graphs depict key features
of various methods (such as the importance of prior knowledge).
